A structure to Manage Data Storage by heirarchy of directory and files


df -Th : check FileSystem

pwd : present working directory
cd {
    cd : change directory to home 
    cd - : go to recent directory
    cd / : go to parent or root directory
    cd DirectoryName : go to spcific directory

}

ls : list folders or files in directory

inode : store metadata about file or folder {
    ls -li : list with inode number
}






